::Prowl/Firearm::

Prowl and Firearm slow their decent through the atmoshphere as they 
approach the Cybertronian Fire, seeing all the ash around. Prowl 
looks at the area, wondering what had happened.

-Love, what's going on?- He thinks to Iron Raptor, approaching the 
Maximal base.
